                                                    To open an image gallery simply:
                                                    <ol>
                                                        <li value="1">Create a link (<![CDATA[&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;]]>).</li>
                                                        <li>Add the rel attribute “prettyPhoto” to it and add your gallery name in square brakets (rel=”prettyPhoto“).</li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Change the href of your link so it points to the 
                                                            <b>full size</b>
                                                            image.</li>
                                                        <li>Pass the following settings when you initialize prettyPhoto: $(“a[rel^=’prettyPhoto’]”).prettyPhoto({theme: ‘facebook’,slideshow:5000, autoplay_slideshow:true});</li>
                                                    </ol>
                                                </div>
