                                                    <a href="/website_prettyPhoto/static/src/img/demo/item2.jpg" rel="prettyPhoto[pp_gal]"><img src="/website_prettyPhoto/static/src/img/demo/item2.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="Red round shape" /></a>
